    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a mechanically sorted example of BMW\u2019s high-revving S54 platform. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six benefits from recent valve clearance adjustments and comprehensive VANOS servicing, ensuring the individual throttle bodies provide crisp, linear response up to the 8,000 RPM redline. Power is managed through a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and the factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis remains taut, featuring professionally reinforced rear subframe mounting points and refreshed suspension bushings to maintain optimal geometry under lateral load. While the exterior displays honest road wear consistent with a well-loved driver's car, the drivetrain and structural components are primed for continued high-performance use. A turn-key opportunity for the enthusiast seeking a pure, analog driving experience.",
