    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of reliability and aesthetic appeal, perfect for someone seeking a dependable daily driver that still turns heads. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish, though a meticulous eye will notice a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small, superficial scuff on the rear passenger door\u2014standard for a car that has been enjoyed on the open road. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and has been strictly smoke-free. The upholstery is in great shape, with only minor softening of the leather on the driver's side bolster. All interior technology, including the touchscreen interface, backup camera, and heated seats, operates exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is in its prime. It has been serviced every 5,000 miles with full synthetic oil, and the most recent inspection confirmed that the brake pads and rotors have significant life remaining. The engine starts promptly and runs quietly, while the transmission provides seamless transitions through all gears. This is a well-documented, honest vehicle that has been cared for with pride of ownership.",
